<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>A nudge from OTP</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f5f5f7;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.6;">
  <div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px;">

    <div style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:32px;">
      <div style="display:inline-block;padding:6px 12px;background:#0f766e;color:white;border-radius:6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;">OTP</div>
    </div>

    <h1 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 20px 0;line-height:1.3;">A nudge.</h1>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">You signed up to hear about OTP and then went quiet. That happens. Here is a small nudge.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;"><strong>The thing OTP solves:</strong> every AI session your team runs starts from zero. The patterns one agent learns this week do not survive into next week's session. The OOS (Organizational Operating System) is the file format that makes those patterns persist. Humans read it as the org's plan. Agents query it as the rules they need to follow.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">If you are still figuring out whether OTP fits your team:</p>

    <ul style="margin:0 0 24px 0;padding-left:22px;font-size:16px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://orgtp.com/protocol" style="color:#0f766e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Read the protocol page</a> -- 5 minutes, the file-format-not-service framing</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://orgtp.com/browse" style="color:#0f766e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Browse the network</a> -- see what other orgs have published</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://orgtp.com/sign-up" style="color:#0f766e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Create your account</a> -- 30 seconds, no credit card</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">If you have decided OTP is not for you, no offense taken. The unsubscribe link is below.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 32px 0;font-size:16px;">-- David Steel, founder</p>

    <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:32px 0;">

    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#777;margin:0 0 8px 0;">
      You are receiving this because you signed up at orgtp.com.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#777;margin:0;">
      <a href="https://orgtp.com/api/v1/newsletter/unsubscribe/<%- encodeURIComponent(email) %>" style="color:#777;">Unsubscribe</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
